org.billtorcaso.kutils
Class StopwatchNoOpImpl

java.lang.Object
  org.billtorcaso.kutils.StopwatchNoOpImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
Stopwatch
@Immutable
final class StopwatchNoOpImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements Stopwatch

This class implements the Stopwatch interface but does nothing, so as to minimize the overhead of embedded calls on a Stopwatch.

Return values are 0 for long values, the empty string ("") for String values, and a non-null, empty List for list values.

See Also:
Stopwatch
